00:56:54.830 --> 00:56:59.120 align:middle line:84%
>> Since I wanted everything to
go naturally, which it didn't--

00:56:59.120 --> 00:57:01.880 align:middle line:84%
chest to chest after
birth experience,

00:57:01.880 --> 00:57:04.940 align:middle line:84%
that didn't happen, because
also I was in a C-section,

00:57:04.940 --> 00:57:06.620 align:middle line:90%
