00:57:36.840 --> 00:57:38.040 align:middle line:90%
these days.

00:57:38.040 --> 00:57:40.770 align:middle line:84%
I took some time off from
work because Keela's still

00:57:40.770 --> 00:57:41.820 align:middle line:90%
in school.

00:57:41.820 --> 00:57:43.710 align:middle line:84%
I spoke with her long
before she had baby,

00:57:43.710 --> 00:57:46.020 align:middle line:84%
