you were when you had her.

00:57:52.560 --> 00:57:55.950 align:middle line:84%
So what you need to do now
is focus, and be positive,

00:57:55.950 --> 00:57:58.980 align:middle line:84%
and live your life
that, when she grows up,

00:57:58.980 --> 00:58:00.610 align:middle line:90%
