00:58:00.610 --> 00:59:42.920 align:middle line:90%


00:59:42.920 --> 00:59:45.770 align:middle line:84%
>> Babies that are born
at very low birth weight--

00:59:45.770 --> 00:59:48.260 align:middle line:90%
that is less than 1,500 grams--

00:59:48.260 --> 00:59:49.260 align:middle line:90%
they're very fragile.

00:59:49.260 --> 00:59:56.860 align:middle line:90%


00:59:56.860 --> 00:59:58.280 align:middle line:84%
For very low birth
weight babies,

00:59:58.280 --> 01:00:00.790 align:middle line:84%
mother's own milk is
not just nutrition.

01:00:00.790 --> 01:00:03.540 align:middle line:90%
It's also medicine.

01:00:03.540 --> 01:00:07.740 align:middle line:84%
It protects them against the
most important complications

01:00:07.740 --> 01:00:10.970 align:middle line:90%
of being born preterm.

01:00:10.970 --> 01:00:12.470 align:middle line:84%
It's really the
most important thing

01:00:12.470 --> 01:00:15.920 align:middle line:84%
that we can do for our patients
to protect their health,

01:00:15.920 --> 01:00:19.550 align:middle line:84%
to promote their growth, and
to promote their long term

01:00:19.550 --> 01:00:20.712 align:middle line:90%
development.

01:00:20.712 --> 01:00:24.020 align:middle line:90%


01:00:24.020 --> 01:00:26.170 align:middle line:84%
It's a very stressful
event to have a baby

01:00:26.170 --> 01:00:28.340 align:middle line:90%
