01:01:17.740 --> 01:01:18.540 align:middle line:90%
option.

01:01:18.540 --> 01:01:24.800 align:middle line:90%


01:01:24.800 --> 01:01:29.780 align:middle line:84%
>> There were milk banks prior
to 1985, and, unfortunately,

01:01:29.780 --> 01:01:32.930 align:middle line:84%
when HIV came, the majority
of the milk banks were closed.

01:01:32.930 --> 01:01:36.240 align:middle line:90%


01:01:36.240 --> 01:01:39.960 align:middle line:84%
It was just a group who saw
the need for donor milk, who

01:01:39.960 --> 01:01:43.140 align:middle line:84%
brought the proposal
forward to the hospital

01:01:43.140 --> 01:01:46.380 align:middle line:84%
administrators, who brought
the proposal forward

01:01:46.380 --> 01:01:49.530 align:middle line:84%
to the Ministry of Health
that allowed us to get funding

01:01:49.530 --> 01:01:51.660 align:middle line:90%
and to build the milk bank.

01:01:51.660 --> 01:01:56.030 align:middle line:90%


01:01:56.030 --> 01:02:02.390 align:middle line:84%
The milk bank first began
dispensing milk in April 2013.

01:02:02.390 --> 01:02:05.360 align:middle line:84%
>> Now I am successfully
pumping my own milk,

01:02:05.360 --> 01:02:06.950 align:middle line:84%
