01:02:21.760 --> 01:02:24.202 align:middle line:90%
And that does calm him down.

01:02:24.202 --> 01:02:27.170 align:middle line:90%


01:02:27.170 --> 01:02:28.970 align:middle line:90%
I am able to touch him.

01:02:28.970 --> 01:02:33.480 align:middle line:84%
I can put my hands around him,
hold his hand, hold his foot.

01:02:33.480 --> 01:02:35.390 align:middle line:84%
And I am really looking
forward to the day

01:02:35.390 --> 01:02:38.180 align:middle line:84%
where I can actually
pick him up and hold him.

