>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

01:04:27.930 --> 01:04:31.080 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

01:04:31.080 --> 01:06:31.800 align:middle line:90%


01:06:31.800 --> 01:06:33.695 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

01:06:33.695 --> 01:07:36.170 align:middle line:90%


01:07:36.170 --> 01:07:40.580 align:middle line:84%
>> From the very start, I really
