post on human milk

01:07:50.300 --> 01:07:52.550 align:middle line:90%
for human babies, Philippines.

01:07:52.550 --> 01:07:56.510 align:middle line:84%
I saw there that there are milk
requests and milk donations.

01:07:56.510 --> 01:07:58.750 align:middle line:90%
And then many mommies--

01:07:58.750 --> 01:08:04.130 align:middle line:84%
they texted me and called
me for their milk donations.

01:08:04.130 --> 01:08:05.210 align:middle line:90%
>> I'm a first time mom.

01:08:05.210 --> 01:08:08.660 align:middle line:84%
I don't have any supply, because
