01:08:30.080 --> 01:08:30.880 align:middle line:90%
that I know.

01:08:30.880 --> 01:08:33.620 align:middle line:84%
I even ask my friends, if
you're breastfeeding, can

01:08:33.620 --> 01:08:36.380 align:middle line:84%
