01:08:49.529 --> 01:08:52.370 align:middle line:90%


01:08:52.370 --> 01:08:55.380 align:middle line:84%
>> I breast fed
108 people babies,

01:08:55.380 --> 01:08:57.830 align:middle line:90%
and I'm proud to be a wet nurse.

01:08:57.830 --> 01:09:00.189 align:middle line:84%
Every time the baby
latches on my breast,

01:09:00.189 --> 01:09:04.420 align:middle line:84%
it feels so fulfilling, and
they're like my children, also.

01:09:04.420 --> 01:09:06.010 align:middle line:90%
I can help him.

01:09:06.010 --> 01:09:10.149 align:middle line:84%
I can give them my best
milk without any question.

01:09:10.149 --> 01:09:13.240 align:middle line:84%
>> I don't have any concerns
about the health conditions

01:09:13.240 --> 01:09:18.490 align:middle line:84%
of the donating mothers, because
I think they are preparing

01:09:18.490 --> 01:09:21.069 align:middle line:90%
their milk for their own babies.

01:09:21.069 --> 01:09:24.050 align:middle line:84%
So it's still safe
for other babies, too.

01:09:24.050 --> 01:09:25.710 align:middle line:90%
>> How about you, Joyce?

01:09:25.710 --> 01:09:29.319 align:middle line:84%
>> I also experience asking
for milk from a stranger.

01:09:29.319 --> 01:09:32.037 align:middle line:84%
I don't know her, but
it takes a lot of guts.

01:09:32.037 --> 01:09:33.120 align:middle line:90%
You don't know the mother.

01:09:33.120 --> 01:09:34.420 align:middle line:90%
You don't know what they eat.

01:09:34.420 --> 01:09:35.712 align:middle line:90%
You don't know their lifestyle.

01:09:35.712 --> 01:09:39.960 align:middle line:84%
