doesn't matter if you know her

01:09:42.870 --> 01:09:43.930 align:middle line:90%
or not.

01:09:43.930 --> 01:09:44.730 align:middle line:90%
It's for your baby.

01:09:44.730 --> 01:10:00.060 align:middle line:90%


01:10:00.060 --> 01:10:02.860 align:middle line:84%
>> It is the responsibility
of the family,

01:10:02.860 --> 01:10:06.930 align:middle line:84%
the community that they should
be given the use of natural

01:10:06.930 --> 01:10:11.280 align:middle line:84%
resources, like
indigenous foods.

01:10:11.280 --> 01:10:14.990 align:middle line:84%
The food is just
around the community.

01:10:14.990 --> 01:10:20.845 align:middle line:84%
Our islands is 7,101 islands
full of calcium rich foods,

01:10:20.845 --> 01:10:23.780 align:middle line:90%
full of protein rich foods.

01:10:23.780 --> 01:10:26.430 align:middle line:84%
It should not be a food
that will disempower,

01:10:26.430 --> 01:10:27.610 align:middle line:90%
especially the mothers.

01:10:27.610 --> 01:10:30.520 align:middle line:90%


01:10:30.520 --> 01:10:34.250 align:middle line:84%
These women are the
ones who are vulnerable.

01:10:34.250 --> 01:10:38.170 align:middle line:84%
They have no power
economically and politically.

01:10:38.170 --> 01:10:42.490 align:middle line:84%
They should be given the
encouragement, the education,

01:10:42.490 --> 01:10:47.240 align:middle line:84%
the latest information on
how to feed their babies.

01:10:47.240 --> 01:10:57.460 align:middle line:90%
[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

01:10:57.460 --> 01:11:02.320 align:middle line:84%
The government should recognize
investing a social support,

01:11:02.320 --> 01:11:06.820 align:middle line:84%
enabling women for
this nurturing power

01:11:06.820 --> 01:11:09.400 align:middle line:90%
to have a healthy population.

01:11:09.400 --> 01:11:16.500 align:middle line:84%
This is the least cost, most
effective, efficient action.

01:11:16.500 --> 01:11:19.300 align:middle line:90%
Respond to their needs.

01:11:19.300 --> 01:11:22.330 align:middle line:84%
Give the mom an access
to appropriate food.

01:11:22.330 --> 01:11:25.732 align:middle line:90%
No child will go hungry.

01:11:25.732 --> 01:11:27.604 align:middle line:90%
[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

