01:12:17.220 --> 01:12:18.600 align:middle line:90%
Women just leave.

01:12:18.600 --> 01:12:22.220 align:middle line:90%


01:12:22.220 --> 01:12:24.350 align:middle line:90%
I said I don't intend to leave.

01:12:24.350 --> 01:12:26.720 align:middle line:90%
I intend to come back to work.

01:12:26.720 --> 01:12:29.800 align:middle line:84%
